Package: nullcat
Type: Package
Title: Null Models for Categorical and Continuous Community Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "Kling", 
           email = "mattkling@berkeley.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Provides null model algorithms for categorical and quantitative 
    community ecology data. Extends classic binary null models (e.g., 
    'curveball', 'swap') to work with categorical data. Provides a stratified
    randomization framework for continuous data.
